  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.69,
    "endTime": 52.73,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.73,
    "endTime": 55.97,
    "text": "-That is messed up. -Right, that's exactly what I thought when he first showed up."
