    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.2,
    "endTime": 58.730000000000004,
    "text": "I mean, how is that not annoying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.73,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Thank you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
